A man accused of killing and secretly burying his wife in a tea plantation has been charged.
  
 ALSO READ:

Man kills 79-year-old woman over radio

 Hillary Okemwa allegedly killed Zipporah Kwamboka before calling his in-laws on Friday night and informing them that she had gone missing.
 The in-laws travelled the following morning and on carrying out a search, discovered a shallow grave in the family's tea plantation.




